---
title: Crispy & Crunchy Tossed Chicken Salad with Creamy Dijon Vinaigrette
description: Looking for a light lunch idea? Here’s a big, crunchy, creamy, and bright salad that’s ready in just 10 minutes and will fuel you right up (without weighing you down). It all starts with chopped mixed greens and crispy cukes. You’ll top that with warmed morsels of juicy, fully cooked chicken—get that lean protein! Add shredded carrots and crunchy croutons and toss it all with a garlicky, tangy Dijon vinaigrette for a meal that’s simple, satisfying, and wholesome as all get-out.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crispy-crunchy-tossed-chicken-salad-d3c655d1.jpg
